  "detailed_description": "Immerse yourself in the classic tower defense gameplay with a delightful blend of strategy and action! Manage turret upgrades, turret placement, coins, and interactables in the midst of the frenzy.<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/7d15e166f6a599c50233c5da5bbf116c.poster.avif?t=1731458800\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/7d15e166f6a599c50233c5da5bbf116c.webm?t=1731458800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/7d15e166f6a599c50233c5da5bbf116c.mp4?t=1731458800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\">         <li> Tailor your towers to your liking, exploring different combos to discover your preferred playstyle. Unlock new maps and towers as you progress, enhancing your arsenal and diversifying your strategic options.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/6ebe192ddfd360ad342fa3ecc1e7097f.poster.avif?t=1731458800\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/6ebe192ddfd360ad342fa3ecc1e7097f.webm?t=1731458800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/6ebe192ddfd360ad342fa3ecc1e7097f.mp4?t=1731458800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li> Each map features interactive objects crucial for dealing with creeps. Strike the right balance between upgrading these tools and fortifying your towers to withstand the relentless onslaught.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/cd1b7ecd0f9e0b551a18747073f987d8.poster.avif?t=1731458800\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/cd1b7ecd0f9e0b551a18747073f987d8.webm?t=1731458800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/cd1b7ecd0f9e0b551a18747073f987d8.mp4?t=1731458800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>    </li><li> Grab bonus coins before they vanish, deciding whether to save up for a game-changing upgrade or spend them immediately to eliminate sneaky wolves.<br>    </li><li>Challenge yourself in Easy or Hard mode and enjoy endless gameplay on any map. Are you prepared to defend against the waves and achieve victory?<br> </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/b0faafc2287a60323157cf0aec20d122.apng?t=1731458800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586240/extras/b0faafc2287a60323157cf0aec20d122.poster.avif?t=1731458800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=81 /></picture></span>",
